3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses neural networks for 3D reconstruction and editing, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a novel approach for integrating rendering into neural networks, which can be considered as an AI technique. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses neural networks for 3D reconstruction and editing, which falls under the domain of neural computing.
